SQL_STMT_U.val: select o.AssetClass,m.ItemCode, ACS1.AcctDtn from itm7 m join oitm o on o.ItemCode=m.ItemCode join ACS1 on ACS1.Code=o.AssetClass and acs1.DprAreaID=m.DprArea join ODTP on ODTP.Code=acs1.DprTypID join ITM8 on itm8.ItemCode=m.ItemCode and itm8.DprArea=m.DprArea and itm8.PeriodCat=m.PeriodCat join ODPV on ODPV.ItemCode=m.ItemCode and ODPV.DprArea=m.DprArea and ODPV.PeriodCat=YEAR(':1') and odpv.SubPeriod=MONTH(':1') where m.RemainLife>0 and ':1' between m.dprStart and m.DprEnd and m.DprArea=':2' order by o.AssetClass

select o.AssetClass,m.ItemCode, ACS1.AcctDtn, ODPV.OrdDprAct from itm7 m join oitm o on o.ItemCode=m.ItemCode join ACS1 on ACS1.Code=o.AssetClass and acs1.DprAreaID=m.DprArea join ODTP on ODTP.Code=acs1.DprTypID join ITM8 on itm8.ItemCode=m.ItemCode and itm8.DprArea=m.DprArea and itm8.PeriodCat=m.PeriodCat join ODPV on ODPV.ItemCode=m.ItemCode and ODPV.DprArea=m.DprArea and ODPV.PeriodCat=YEAR(':1') and odpv.SubPeriod=MONTH(':1') where m.RemainLife>0 and ':1' between m.dprStart and m.DprEnd and m.DprArea=':2' order by o.AssetClass
